$$5 m+3(9+3 m)=2(7 m-11)$$

Distribute.
$$5 m+27+9 m=14 m-22$$

Combine like terms.
$$14 m+27=14 m-22$$

Subtract $14 m$ from both sides. $14 m+27-14 m=14 m-22-14 m$

> Simplify.

But $27 \neq-22$.
$$27 \neq-22$$

The equation is a contradiction.
